Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: Any non-evil alignment, 12 Charisma.
Specifics: You can channel the power of your faith and energy to enhance a single attack you make. You gain a bonus equal to your Charisma bonus on the attack roll and damage roll for the next melee attack you make against an outsider. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to your Charisma bonus.

Use: Selected.